data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Blythewood! Stunning 5BR/2.5BA residence, nestled within the sought-after Amber Creek Subdivision, offers the perfect blend of convenience & tranquility. Just minutes from I-77, this property places you in the midst of all things Blythewood, while providing a serene escape from the hustle and bustle. Boasting an incredible floor plan that maximizes space, this home welcomes you with an inviting ambiance. A dedicated office with French doors, a formal dining room & chef's delight kitchen equipped with 42" Birch cabinetry, granite countertops, spacious eat-in breakfast area & stainless-steel appliances are just a few highlights of this remarkable property. The family room is a true focal point, adorned with built-ins, elegant columns & charming arch accents, creating a space that is both functional and aesthetically pleasing. Retreat to the primary bedroom featuring a private balcony & gorgeous ensuite bathroom, offering a perfect oasis within your own home. Step outside to discover a private backyard that will exceed the expectations of any homeowner. This well maintained residence is a testament to quality and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own.  Contact our team today!
